w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103433\/Livraria-Lello-port3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The gothic exterior of the building is so detailed with its stone carvings, and religious-looking paintings, that it looks more like a church from the outside than a bookstore. However, once you walk through the door you see art-nouveau style design in everything from the walls and columns to the curves of the staircase.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/porto-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Things to do in Porto!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto.jpg\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\" class=\"wp-image-58846 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103454\/Livraria-Lello-porto-512x768.jpg 512w, https