    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Don&#x2019;t forget to look up! There is a huge stained glass window on the ceiling with the words &#x2018;decus in labore&#x2019;. This was the Lello brother&#x2019;s motto, meaning &#x2018;honor in work&#x2019;. Also, you&#x2019;ll see carved wood across the ceiling. However, this is actually a clever technique of painting plaster to make it look like wood.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/58713&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12111650\/livraria-lello-porto-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12111650\/livraria-lello-porto-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12111650\/livraria-lello-porto-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Livraria Lello, Porto: The Famous &#x2018;Harry Potter&#x2019; Bookstore\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-livraria-lello-the-inspiration-for-harry-potter\">Livraria Lello: The Inspiration for Harry Potter?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The story goes that Livraria Lello is actually the inspiration behind some of the famous Hogwarts scenery in Harry Potter. This story began when JK Rowling used to live in Porto as an English teacher, visiting the bookstore at the weekend. It&#x2019;s easy to see how this story could be true, with the magical feeling of the bookstore, the bookshelves, and the &#x2018;floating&#x2019; staircases and bridges.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2.jpg\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\" class=\"wp-image-58850 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c