lock-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-opening-hours-livraria-lello\">Opening Hours Livraria Lello<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Monday:<\/strong> closed<br><strong>Tuesday to Sunday:<\/strong> open 10:30 AM &#x2013; 7:30 PM<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Especially in the summer, queues can be very long because it&#x2019;s high season in Porto. The shoulder seasons of spring and autumn are the perfect time to visit! However, the benefit of the ticket system is that the staff can control the number of people inside. As a result, it&#x2019;s much easier to enjoy the atmosphere of the bookstore and get some great photos.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-photography-tips\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">14 Travel Photography Tips to Improve your Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-how-to-get-to-lello-bookstore-in-porto\">How to get to Lello Bookstore in Porto<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/place\/Livraria+Lello\/@41.1469055,-8.6147746,15z\/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0x7f08405ee8a1e44f?sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj46Pmel8HwAhUGhv0HHSwSAEsQ_BIwHXoECDEQBQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">location<\/a> of Livraria Lello. It is located next to the University and the Clerigos Towers and is just a 10-minute walk from Sao Bento Station.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-ima